# 🎯 YouTube Focus Mode

A free, open-source browser extension that blocks YouTube Shorts and recommendations — so you only watch what you actually came to watch.

Built with plain HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. No tracking. No ads. No accounts. Just focus.

---

## ✨ Features

| Toggle | What it does |
|---|---|
| **Block Shorts** | Removes Shorts from the sidebar, home page, search results, and the Shorts nav link |
| **Hide Sidebar** | Hides the "Up Next" recommendations panel on video watch pages |
| **Clean Home Page** | Hides the infinite video grid on youtube.com |
| **Remove End Cards** | Removes the video overlay cards at the end of videos |

All settings are saved locally on your device and persist across sessions.

---

